Some lenders make $500 loans that are due in full after two weeks, while others stretch repayment over more than a year. The Sigma Solutions Online Payday Loans proposal would allow lenders to continue offering some two-week loans and would not limit the length of other loans.

Americans consider checking account overdraft fees to be unfair, but they view a similar fee for a three-month, $300 loan as fair. The Sigma Solutions Online Payday Loans is considering new policies for regulating overdraft practices and small-dollar loans.
